definition: to add/to attach/to be close to/to be attached
abbr. for Canada 加拿大[Jia1 na2 da4]/surname Jia

to add/plus/(used after an adverb such as 不, 大, 稍 etc, and before a disyllabic verb, to indicate that the action of the verb is applied to sth or sb previously mentioned)/to apply (restrictions etc) to (sb)/to give (support, consideration etc) to (sth)

sentences.english: A few abilities have had the duration of the secondary effects extended, such as Dragon's Talon.
sentences.chinese: 一些技能的附加效果持續時間被延長，如巨龍鉤爪。

sentences.english: The etymological meaning of both words is “something added on.”
sentences.chinese: 從詞源學的角度來看，兩個詞都有“附加物”的意思。

sentences.english: Above prices are in MOP and are subject to 10% service charge.
sentences.chinese: 以上價目以澳門幣結算，需附加10%的服務費。

sentences.english: I found a serious bug in my add-on, and I really want to get the fix up there quickly.
sentences.chinese: 我的附加組件已經發布，用戶看上去很喜歡。

sentences.english: Where now there is additional pressure here.
sentences.chinese: 現在這裏有附加的壓強。

sentences.english: The coffret provides strong added value to personal care products.
sentences.chinese: 與套裝提供了強有力的附加價值，個人護理產品。

sentences.english: Learn how to attach the chimney to a birdhouse in this free video about making birdhouses.
sentences.chinese: 瞭解如何在這個自由附加視頻煙囪一禽舍有關使鳥屋。

sentences.english: There is also an additional global run queue where new threads are placed.
sentences.chinese: 還有一個附加的全局運行隊列，其中放的是新的線程。

sentences.english: Additional debug tools provide advanced users to dig deeper into TexTools.
sentences.chinese: 提供了附加的排錯工具給用戶進行更深層次的開發。

sentences.english: But there's another meaning given to shepherds as well.
sentences.chinese: 但是還有另一個附加在牧羊人上的含義。

sentences.english: The finite volume discretization method and treatment of boundary condition were presented.
sentences.chinese: 採用有限容積法離散方程，附加源項法處理邊界條件。

sentences.english: The following section first shows how to enrich outliers with additional information.
sentences.chinese: 接下來的小節首先展示如何用附加信息擴展離羣值。

sentences.english: The firm had a major storehouse attached to its factory in Walsall.
sentences.chinese: 該公司有一個大倉庫附加到其工廠在沃爾薩爾。

sentences.english: Sony’s additional screen layers make the E Ink less sharp.
sentences.chinese: 索尼附加的屏幕層讓電子墨水的顯示效果不夠銳利。

sentences.english: Attach objects to ropes with figure eight follow through knots.
sentences.chinese: 與圖八個對象附加到結繩循。

sentences.english: To show additional information that may be linked intrinsically to an element.
sentences.chinese: 顯示可能內在地鏈接到某個元素的附加信息。
